{"id":"libni","term":"Libni","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>White, one of the two sons of Gershon, the son of Levi (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 6:17\">Ex. 6:17</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 3:18\">Num. 3:18</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 3:21\">21</a>). (See LAADAN.)</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Exodus 6:17","Numbers 3:18","Numbers 3:21"]}